@node Main "S_Tiles - Documentation"

                              'S_Tiles' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'S_Tiles' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} based on the popular 4 by 4
sliding-tiles-puzzle but with a little difference: In addition to
the normal sliding moves, you can @{" move " link play} a tile from one edge of
the board so it can 'wrap-around' to the opposed edge (of course,
the empty space must be on the other side).

  The @{" goal " link play} is simple: try to put the numbered tiles in the right
order in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
